steps.name: Launch the browser login to the application
Click on the API Environment button the ManageEnvironments page
Click on the Add New Environment button index page is displayed
Enter all valid credentials into create environment screen
Click on the save button manage variable screen is displayed
Click on pickfrom API and enter response
Click on save button data rule screen displayed
Click on back button the index page is displayed
